&lt;copy&gt;&lt;paste&gt;<br>
<br>
----------------------<br>
GUILD FACTION GUIDE<br>
----------------------<br>
<br>
Train Points<br>
=========<br>
+2 for training<br>
+3 for training and taking the trainee's camp<br>
+4 for training a raid<br>
+3 for training the guild<br>
+5 for training the guild during a raid<br>
+10 for training a Guide<br>
+25 for training a GM<br>
<br>
-1 for not training when you have the opportunity to <br>
-2 for not training the guild when you can<br>
-5 for not training during a raid when you can<br>
<br>
Pulling<br>
=====<br>
+1 for pulling when people say don't pull<br>
+1 for saying you are pulling when you are actually hiding and afk<br>
+2 for pulling mobs that only benefit you<br>
+2 for pulling 4 or more mobs but sayin you have 1<br>
+1 per afk person for pulls of 4 or more when you say you have 1<br>
<br>
Pulling and training points do NOT stack! Take the highest<br>
<br>
&quot;Reputation points&quot;<br>
==============<br>
+1 point for each /ooc or /shout that bashes YourGuildX due to your train or pull - max of 5 per pull/train<br>
+2 for KSing or Campstealing that gets an /ooc or a /shout that is anti-YourGuildX - max 2 points<br>
+3 for a ninja that does the same as above<br>
+1 for a PK, this will stack with other PK points to be covered further down<br>
+3 points for ripping someone off in a trade where they get an inferior deal<br>
+5 for straight ripping them off and giving them nothing<br>
<br>
-2 if somone in your group says anything good about YourGuildX<br>
-5 if they say that because of you<br>
<br>
Ninja points<br>
=========<br>
+1 for a basic ninja<br>
+2 for an item worth 3K or more<br>
+3 for an item worht 10K or more<br>
+5 for a great item that you can't use or equip<br>
+10 for an Epic component<br>
+8 for God or Dragon loot<br>
bump +5 if it's No Drop<br>
<br>
-5 for giving an item back or MQing<br>
-10 for giving Dragon/God loot back<br>
-25 if it is an Epic component you give back<br>
<br>
PKing<br>
====<br>
+1 per PK<br>
+2 if its a Guildie<br>
0 for Rangers and Enchanters<br>
<br>
These do not stack with Train/Pull points but do with Reputation points<br>
